15 WHEREAS, a compassionate, hardworking, and protective man, Officer Labonte will long
16 be remembered for his love of family and friendship, and this loyal husband, brother, and
17 friend will be missed by all who had the great fortune of knowing him; and
18 WHEREAS, Officer Labonte exhibited extraordinary devotion to public service, outstanding
19 loyalty, fine leadership, and meticulous attention to detail in all of his duties and it is
20 abundantly fitting and proper that this remarkable and distinguished Georgian be recognized
21 appropriately by dedicating an interchange in his memory.
22 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED AND ENACTED BY THE GENERAL
23 ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA that the interchange of State Route 400/US 19 and State Route
24 140/Holcomb Bridge Road in Fulton County is dedicated as the Officer Jeremy Labonte
25 Memorial Interchange.
26 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Department of Transportation is authorized and
27 directed to erect and maintain appropriate signs dedicating the Officer Jeremy Labonte
28 Memorial Interchange.
29 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
30 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the family of
31 Officer Jeremy Labonte and to the Department of Transportation.
